
### Pillar 2 cases {.tabset}

#### By region
```{r reg-pillar2, cache=TRUE, cache.extra=results_hash}
stop()
dim.id <- which(names(dimnames(noisy_case)) == "date")
noisy_case <- extract(noisy_case, indices = list(start.gp:end.gp), dims = dim.id)
case.dat <- case.dat %>%
	 filter(date >= start.date - 1 + start.gp,
	 	date <= start.date - 1 + end.gp)
make.plots(noisy_case, by = "region", data = case.dat)
```

#### By age
```{r}
make.plots(noisy_case, by = "age", data = case.dat)
```

